Package mg.mapviewer.model

This package contains all classes to model the track data.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MultiPointModel
    A simple model for multiple points
    PointModel
    A model for a single point
    WriteableMultiPointModel
    A writeable model for multiple points.
    WriteablePointModel
    A point model with changeable model data
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BBox
    A bounding box implementation
    MetaData  
    MultiPointModelImpl
    An implementation of a writeable model for multiple points.
    PointModelImpl
    A simple implementation for a single point
    TrackLog
    A TrackLog consists of multiple TrackLogSegment objects, a total TrackLogStatistic over all segments and a track log name
    TrackLogPoint
    Stores the data of a single point of a TrackLog.
    TrackLogRef
    Reference on a TrackLog (and a particular Segment of it).
    TrackLogRefApproach
    A specific kind of TrackLogRef to reference an approach to a TrackLog.
    TrackLogRefZoom
    A specific kind of TrackLogRef to reference a TrackLog.
    TrackLogSegment
    A TrackLogSegment contains additionally to the points in the MultiPointModel a few more data.
    TrackLogStatistic
    Statistic of a TrackLog or of a Segment of a TrackLog.
    WriteablePointModelImpl
    A implementation of a point model with changeable model data
    WriteableTrackLog
    Creates new TrackLog objects based on existing GPX data, requires special handling with the timestamps.

Package mg.mapviewer.model Description

This package contains all classes to model the track data.
